text: From the Czech Mills (Z ceských mlýnu) is a 1941 Czechoslovak comedy film, directed by Miroslav Cikán. It stars Theodor Pištěk, Jindřich Plachta, and Svatopluk Beneš. ==References== ==External links== *From the Czech Mills at the Internet Movie Database Category:1941 films Category:Czechoslovak films Category:Czechoslovak comedy films Category:1941 comedy films Category:Films directed by Miroslav Cikán Category:Czech films Category:Czechoslovak black- and-white films
